76	  \item Definition~\ref{def:Pic_functor} (Picard functor of $C/k$) — quotient by $\Pic(S)$ uses Theorem~\ref{thm:Scheme_Pic_pullback}.
77	  \item Theorem~\ref{thm:Pic_representable} (representability of the Picard scheme) — uses the full $\Pic$ machinery built here.
78	  \item Definition~\ref{def:ofCurve} (Abel--Jacobi map) — defined via the line bundle $\mathcal O_{C \times C}(\Delta - p_1^* P)$ on $C \times C$, an explicit element of $\Pic(C \times C)$.
