616	  \]
617	  This is the bridge from the geometric input (the bundled affine cover $S$) to the categorical input (a $\MayerVietorisSquare$) the abstract MV-LES theorem $\HModulePrime\_\mathtt{sequence\_exact}$ consumes.
618	\end{definition}
619	
620	\begin{lemma}[Corner identifications, iter-028]
