570	During iter-043 plan-agent scoping the H${}^0$ Hom-finiteness chain was re-examined and a critical mis-design in iter-041's carrier surfaced. By the Yoneda + free-functor + sheafify chain of adjunctions, the iter-041 class field
571	\[
572	  \mathtt{module\_finite\_hom} : \forall \{U\}, \mathtt{IsAffineOpen}\,U \to \Module.\mathrm{Finite}\,k\,((\mathtt{presheafToSheaf}).\mathtt{obj}((\mathtt{yoneda}\circ\mathtt{free}_k).\mathtt{obj}\,U) \to F)
