744	\begin{proof}
745	  Build the $\LinearEquiv$ structure by overriding the \lstinline{map_smul'} field of \lstinline{adj.homAddEquiv}: the $\mathtt{change}$ tactic exposes the underlying $\mathtt{homEquiv}$ form, after which $\mathtt{simp}\,[\mathtt{adj.homEquiv\_unit}]$ closes via the same naturality argument as Lemma~\ref{lemma:Adjunction_left_adjoint_linear}. The \lstinline{haveI} line that establishes $F.\mathtt{Linear}\,R$ via Lemma~\ref{lemma:Adjunction_left_adjoint_linear} is load-bearing.
