201	\label{sec:moduleK_cech}
202	
203	This section opens Path~2 of Phase~A step~6: the \v{C}ech-cohomology approach to Serre finiteness. The \v{C}ech complex of a sheaf with respect to an indexed open cover is the standard alternating-coface complex; its cohomology in each degree lives in the category of $k$-modules.
