  Let $C$ be a scheme over $\Spec k$ and $S$ a two-affine cover of $C$. If $H^{\prime n}(S.\toMayerVietorisSquare.X_4, \mathcal O_C)$ is finite-dimensional over $k$, then so is $H^{n}(C, \mathcal O_C)$.
