880:\section{Čech acyclicity for the structure sheaf on affine basic-open covers}
881-\label{sec:basic_open_acyclicity}
882-
883-Let $X$ be a $k$-scheme, $U \subseteq X$ an affine open, and $s \subseteq \mathcal O_X(U)$ a set generating the unit ideal. Write $\mathfrak U = \{D(f)\}_{f \in s}$ for the basic-open cover. The Čech cochain complex of the structure sheaf with respect to $\mathfrak U$ is
884-\[
885-  C^n(\mathfrak U, \mathcal O_X) \;=\; \prod_{(f_0,\dots,f_n) \in s^{n+1}} \mathcal O_X\bigl(D(f_0) \cap \cdots \cap D(f_n)\bigr),
886-\]
887-with the standard alternating-coface differential.
